    "mechanics": [
      {
        "name": "Active_Camo.exe",
        "moreInfo": {
          "model": "gear",
          "id": "active-camo-exe"
        },
        "type": "other",
        "shortDesc": "When on, Wisdom (Perception) checks made to see you have disadvantage and you have advantage on Dexterity (Stealth) checks made to hide.",
        "toggle": {
          "id": "active-camo-exe",
          "whenOn": [
            {
              "type": "skill-check",
              "value": "stealth",
              "effect": {
                "type": "advantage",
                "note": "to hide"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "html": "<p>The user's omni-tool diverts energy to coat their armor in color-adaptive hard light, using\ndata obtained from the suit's micro-sensors. While not making the wearer truly invisible, this adaptive camouflage helps\nthe user blend into any environment. Wisdom (Perception) checks made to see you have disadvantage and you have\nadvantage on Dexterity (Stealth) checks made to hide. You can use a free action to toggle this effect on or off.</p>\n",
    "id": "active-camo-exe"
  },
